OL,3,GNEWSCChanges to BBC News channel output
OL,4,C"not recreating or competing with BBC
OL,5,CBreakfast"
OL,6,
OL,7,FAs reported on Clean Feed yesterday,
OL,8,Fthe UK version of the BBC News channel
OL,9,Fwill replace BBC Breakfast with live
OL,10,Fnews programming from its international
OL,11,Fequivalent from tomorrow morning ` this
OL,12,Fhas now been confirmed in an e-mail to
OL,13,Fstaff.
OL,15,FProgramme listings were updated
OL,16,Fyesterday afternoon to reflect the
OL,17,Fchange.
