OL,5,CBreakfast"
OL,6,
OL,7,Fb@XComing Up' sequences will be used at
OL,8,F.15, .26, .45 and .56 "to bring energy,
OL,9,Fmomentum and promote good content".
OL,11,FThe business presenter will provide
OL,12,Fheadlines at 7am and 8am.
OL,14,FGlobal front pages (newspapers and
OL,15,Fwebsites) "to be used as a production
OL,16,Fdevice around big stories", with a more
OL,17,Fin-depth look at 6.51am.
OL,19,FThere will be pushbacks, promoting
OL,20,Fnewsletters, BBC Local and BBC Radio 5
OL,21,FLive, for the UK audience.
